{
  "text": "With newer treatment techniques, such as the breath-hold technique, intensity-modulated RT, particle therapy, and volumetric-modulated arc therapy, IMNI can be delivered at even lower doses to the organ at risk, especially in left-sided breast cancer [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Consequently, the incidence of RP and dose parameters with IMNI estimated in this study can be further decreased by including these newer methods.",
  "correct_citation": {
